<l>kaṇṇā vāṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>maṇṇōr viṇṇōrkkut</l>
<l>taṇṇār vēṅkaṭa</l>
<l>viṇṇōr veṟpaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who always is eye is the lord</l>
<l>of the celestials’ Vēṅkaṭa mountain</l>
<l>filled with coolness,</l>
<l>for those of the earth [and] the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
